N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 16.9 - Renewals

State Regulations

The registrant of a vehicle to which a special number plate
has been assigned shall have the right to renew such registration, within one
year of the expiration thereof, and to retain such special number plate, unless
otherwise barred by statute or by this Part. Notes
